titles: A continuation of the acts and monuments of our late Parliament: or, A collection of the acts, orders, votes, and resolves that hath passed in the House. From June 9 to July 7. 1659. By J. Canne Intelligencer Generall.
author: Butler, Samuel, 1612-1680,
Canne, John, d. 1667?,
notes: Not in fact by John Canne, but rather a satirical attack on Canne and the Parliament; sometimes attributed to Samuel Butler.
